    <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Reporting accessibility problems with this website</h2>
    <p class="govuk-body long-link">
        We’re always looking to improve the accessibility of this website. If you find any problems not listed on this page or think we’re not meeting accessibility requirements, emailing <br />
        <a class="govuk-link" href="mailto:fellinglicenceonline@forestrycommission.gov.uk">fellinglicenceonline@forestrycommission.gov.uk</a>
    </p>

    <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Enforcement procedure</h2>
    <p class="govuk-body">
        The Equality and Human Rights Commission (EHRC) is responsible for enforcing the Public Sector Bodies (Websites and Mobile Applications) (No. 2) Accessibility Regulations 2018 (the 'accessibility regulations').
        If you're not happy with how we respond to your complaint, 
        <a href="https://www.equalityadvisoryservice.com/" class="govuk-link">contact the Equality Advisory and Support Service (EASS) (opens in new tab)</a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Technical information about this website’s accessibility</h2>
    <p class="govuk-body">The Forestry Commission is committed to making its websites and applications accessible, in accordance with the Public Sector Bodies (Websites and Mobile Applications) (No. 2) Accessibility Regulations 2018.</p>

    <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Content that’s not within the scope of the accessibility regulations</h2>
    <p class="govuk-body">PDFs, documents and attachments to email notifications published before 23 September 2018 may not meet accessibility standards. For example, they may not be structured so they’re accessible to a screen reader.</p>
    
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Third party content that’s under someone else’s control</h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">Pages and websites that are linked to and from the probate service may not be fully accessible.</p>
    <p class="govuk-body">These include:</p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>external pages hosting PDF documents</li>
        <li>login pages</li>
        <li>emails sent by gov.uk notify</li>
        <li>instruction pages on gov.uk</li>
	</ul>

    <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">What we’re doing to improve accessibility</h2>
    <p class="govuk-body long-link">
        We are keen to engage with users of this service and to continue to develop this application to meet the needs of our users. Performance of this application will be regularly assessed, and accessibility reviewed every 12 months in September.
		If you have any experience or information relating to the use of this, or a similar service, which would help us better meet the needs of our users, please email us at  <br />
        <a class="govuk-link" href="mailto:fellinglicenceonline@forestrycommission.gov.uk">fellinglicenceonline@forestrycommission.gov.uk</a>
    </p>

